# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
addons/*.pbo
addons/*.bisign
keys/*.biprivatekey

# ── Signing key (belt-and-suspenders: catch it anywhere in the tree) ──────────
*.biprivatekey

# ── Server deploy artifacts (live server files, not source) ───────────────────
# These are deployed by 2_deploy.bat — don't track the deployed copies
/deploy/

# ── Secrets / credentials ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
serverDZ.cfg
*.cfg
BEServer*.cfg

# ── DayZ Tools intermediate files ────────────────────────────────────────────
*.bak
*.log
P:\

# ── Unpacked vanilla game data (reference only — copyrighted, never commit) ────
.vanilla_ref/

# ── Claude Code internal files ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# ── Local-only planning docs (kept locally, never committed) ──────────────────
PUBLISHING.md
SEPARATION_PLAN.md

# ── One-off local tooling (not part of the mod's build pipeline) ──────────────
make_icon.py
make_icon.bat

# ── OS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini

# ── Editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
*.suo
*.user
